{"abstract":[{"text":"Audio units unleash the power of iPhone OS to provide your app with sophisticated audio manipulation and processing. Dive deep into the architecture and fundamentals of an app built around audio units and understand how to take advantage of their richness in your own code. Learn to use audio units for mixing, and see how your app can support low-latency input and output.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/413\/","type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","isActive":true},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10-413-Audio-Development-for-iPhone-OS-Part-2","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10-413-audio-development-for-iphone-os-part-2"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC10","role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Audio Development for iPhone OS, Part 2"},"references":{"WWDC10.jpeg":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC10.jpeg","alt":null,"type":"image"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/im